<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-3271] Incomplete widths array for CID-fonts</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3271</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In my day job I&apos;ve migrated a project to PDFBox 2.0.0 and found an issue with CID-fonts. The created width array is incomplete in some non deterministic constellations, so that the default width is used for the missing CIDs. In my case spaces had a doubled width which lead to a false rendering.&lt;br/&gt;
Furthermore the CIDs aren&apos;t sorted so that the resulting width array might not be optimal&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12949692">PDFBOX-3271</key>
            <summary>Incomplete widths array for CID-fonts</summary>
